com.strategyobject.substrateclient.pallet.storage

Interface PagedKeyIterator<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the value.

    public interface PagedKeyIterator<V>
    An iterator of key collection. Each element in the sequence contains a key collection with size equal to the page's size or smaller in case of the last page and the total number isn't multiple of tbe page's size.
